divs: Sighting DetailsI was riding my bikecycle on green bay road north in kenosha Wis. I was about 100 meters or 75 meters from Highway 50 which ran east an west. The UFO was headed east towards the Lake Michagan, traveling just above little clouds, it was just befor dark sun was setting and cloudy it just stopped about 300 feet in the air i pointed at it so people in their cars would stop to see what i seen. next i just drop my bike and ran under some trees near a house. the UFO just went east quickly an quitly after i started running under the trees. in June 18 or 19 of 1978 .
